response.overview: On November 4th GCW: Si or No? is live on FITE+ straight from Center Stage Theater in Atlanta, GA. The event features the GCW World Title Match where Blake Christian (c) defends his title against Tank.  Also in the lineup:  Six Man Tag Team Match  Maki Death BUSSY (Allie Katch, Effy & Maki Itoh) vs Young Dumb And Bros (August Matthews, Davey Bang & Jordan Oliver)  Gringo Loco vs Masha Slamovich  Mike Jackson vs Charles Mason w/ Parrow  Joey Janela vs Jacob Fatu  Tag Team Match  The Second Gear Crew (1 Called Manders & Mance Warner) vs BULLET CLUB War Dogs (Alex Coughlin & Gabe Kidd)  GCW Tag Team Title Match  Los Macizos (Ciclope & Miedo Extremo) (c) vs Violence Is Forever (Dominic Garrini & Kevin Ku)  Jimmy Lloyd vs Steph De Lander  Mike Bailey vs Santana Jackson
response.title: GCW Si or No?
